# Next.js & React

## Versions
- Next.js **16.1.6** with the App Router (`src/app/`)
- React **19.2.3**
- Package manager: **pnpm**

## Documentation
- Canonical docs: https://nextjs.org/docs
- Always reference these docs for API usage, conventions, and best practices

## Conventions
- Prefer React Server Components by default; add `"use client"` only when client interactivity is needed
- Use `next/image` for images, `next/font` for fonts, and `next/link` for navigation
- Follow App Router file conventions: `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `loading.tsx`, `error.tsx`, `route.ts`
- Prefer Route Handlers (`app/**/route.ts`) for API calls over Server Actions
